nodes.text: Yongti was a princess of a Nightsister clan on the planet Dathomir. During a raid to steal males of breeding suitability from a rival clan, she tried to capture Jedi Knight Quinlan Vos, who was masquerading as a slave. Yongti and her rancor were killed under fire from one of Queen Zalem's tunneling machines, piloted by Vonya.
